OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly cloudy but dry start
OL,6,Fto the day. Cloud breaking up through
OL,7,Fthe morning, allowing warm and sunny
OL,8,Fspells to develop. Winds mostly light.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FDry overnight with some cloud
OL,11,Faround to start the evening, but long
OL,12,Fclear spells soon developing through
OL,13,Fthe night. Mild with light winds.
OL,14,
OL,15,CFriday:FBecoming warm or very warm on
OL,16,FFriday with plenty of sunshine,
OL,17,Falthough this may turn hazy at times.
OL,18,FMild overnight with a risk of showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
